creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
WELCOME to the Official First Presbyterian Church of Tacoma APP!

Here you will find various resources including sermons, information on upcoming events, upcoming class info, a church calendar and other useful information.

Our Mission is to glorify God by serving our neighbors, upholding Biblical truth, and growing in Christ together.

Our Core Values are;
Relationships: Devote ourselves to people through the seasons of life.
Children: Prioritize children & youth and equip them to live Christ centered lives.
Missions: Bring people near and far to a life transforming relationship with Christ.
Truth: Uphold the Bible as truth and share that truth.
Discipleship: Help people mature spiritually and exercise their spiritual gifts.

For more information about First Presbyterian Church
please visit: www.fpctacoma.org

The FPC App was developed with the Subsplash App platform
descriptionShort: The FPC app features various resources to connect you and keep you informed.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel
- Administers can set channels to be public for anyone to join

Fixed:
- Media playback now stops when you force close the app
- Fixed a Messaging issue causing link previews to cause the channel to crash
